      "date": "2019-03-15 05:10:23.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: Verified-1\n\nPassed enforced test review-dne-part-1 on CentOS 7.0/x86_64 uploaded by AT Release Candidate from trevis-67vm7: https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/dfd788f1-8c6e-49e0-9635-0c4f2c3a4983 ran 6 tests.",
